=== Realtime Graphite ===
To see [[Graphite]] graphs in a per-second resolution. 
====  /opt/graphite/conf/storage-schemas.conf ====
 [real_time]
 priority = 200
 pattern = ^realtime.*
 retentions = 1s:365d

